1
00:01:44,340 --> 00:01:48,800
[A LOVER IN THE MORTAL WORLD]

2
00:01:49,530 --> 00:01:51,590
[Episode 3]

3
00:01:57,229 --> 00:01:58,229
Guys,

4
00:01:59,350 --> 00:02:00,590
bring me more wine.

5
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,760
Your Majesty, you're in a good mood.

6
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,280
Sister,

7
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:05,840
why are you here?

8
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:07,950
I knew you were out of wine,

9
00:02:08,210 --> 00:02:09,479
so I brought you some.

10
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:11,870
You are so kind to me.

11
00:02:14,030 --> 00:02:14,840
Sister,

12
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,360
I

13
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,520
toast you.

14
00:02:19,030 --> 00:02:20,310
You have grown up.

15
00:02:21,030 --> 00:02:22,760
Learned to drown your sorrows.

16
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,150
No.

17
00:02:24,710 --> 00:02:25,560
Okay.

18
00:02:26,430 --> 00:02:27,360
I

19
00:02:27,890 --> 00:02:29,350
will have a drink with you.

20
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:41,680
What's up, Your Majesty?

21
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,310
The sky is so beautiful.

22
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,240
And there is good wine.

23
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,680
But you seem

24
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,960
in low spirits.

25
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:52,079
With you here,

26
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,530
nothing could make me unhappy.

27
00:02:55,190 --> 00:02:57,240
I raised you since you were little.

28
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,590
I know your feelings

29
00:02:58,750 --> 00:03:00,240
at a glance.

30
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,000
You don't have to

31
00:03:02,150 --> 00:03:03,800
hide anything from me.

32
00:03:04,190 --> 00:03:06,240
Just tell me what happened.

33
00:03:06,710 --> 00:03:07,520
Sister,

34
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:09,230
do you

35
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,400
ever think

36
00:03:13,510 --> 00:03:16,070
I am not cut out to be an emperor?

37
00:03:19,470 --> 00:03:20,200
Why would you

38
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:22,430
think that suddenly?

39
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:25,420
When our father was on the throne,

40
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:28,150
his majesty and decisiveness

41
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,430
made all the subjects

42
00:03:30,430 --> 00:03:32,079
submit to him.

43
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,800
But I think...

44
00:03:36,310 --> 00:03:37,470
I can't do that.

45
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,560
You just ascended the throne.

46
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:46,590
Naturally, you can't

47
00:03:46,590 --> 00:03:48,190
compare with him right away.

48
00:03:48,710 --> 00:03:50,150
But I believe

49
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:51,870
one day,

50
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:53,970
you will awe the subjects

51
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,280
like our father.

52
00:03:55,300 --> 00:03:57,610
But I don't want to awe them at all.

53
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,800
I always feel that

54
00:04:01,190 --> 00:04:02,630
a high position

55
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:05,460
comes with heavy responsibilities.

56
00:04:05,470 --> 00:04:06,720
The court

57
00:04:07,030 --> 00:04:09,440
should be united.

58
00:04:11,670 --> 00:04:13,160
Are you worried

59
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:15,160
that the veteran officials

60
00:04:15,910 --> 00:04:16,769
are hard to control?

61
00:04:16,769 --> 00:04:18,180
I need to consult

62
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:20,800
them about something,

63
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:22,600
but…

64
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:25,720
But you don't like them
dominating the court.

65
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:34,320
These three veterans, Zhang, Wang, and Li,

66
00:04:34,610 --> 00:04:36,470
have always assisted our father.

67
00:04:37,159 --> 00:04:38,550
In the court,

68
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:39,960
they are deeply rooted.

69
00:04:40,140 --> 00:04:41,700
Father also entrusted you to their care.

70
00:04:41,700 --> 00:04:42,770
I know that

71
00:04:42,990 --> 00:04:46,730
since you just ascended the throne,
you haven't wielded absolute power.

72
00:04:46,730 --> 00:04:47,620
But

73
00:04:49,370 --> 00:04:51,610
I will always be by your side

74
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,480
and assist you.

75
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:57,840
You are so kind to me.

76
00:05:02,010 --> 00:05:02,760
Come on.

77
00:05:05,090 --> 00:05:05,800
Come on.

78
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:08,390
I believe in you.

79
00:05:08,410 --> 00:05:10,810
You will definitely revitalize the court,

80
00:05:10,900 --> 00:05:12,560
bring honor to the Liu family,

81
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:14,930
and restore our father's glory.

82
00:05:16,310 --> 00:05:17,120
Okay.

83
00:05:18,610 --> 00:05:20,320
Since you said so,

84
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:23,390
I won't let you

85
00:05:23,750 --> 00:05:25,680
and our father down.

86
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:39,400
Fei Zheng.

87
00:05:40,550 --> 00:05:41,230
Tell me.

88
00:05:42,690 --> 00:05:44,690
How did we become enemies?

89
00:05:46,830 --> 00:05:47,680
Indeed.

90
00:06:08,790 --> 00:06:09,990
The two

91
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:12,240
seem to be a good match.

92
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:19,070
Sister.

93
00:06:20,790 --> 00:06:23,470
I really miss when we were little.

94
00:06:24,070 --> 00:06:25,310
Back then,

95
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,930
Mother was still alive.

96
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,920
Our whole family

97
00:06:30,060 --> 00:06:32,180
was together.

98
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,640
Times flies.

99
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,960
You and I

100
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:43,010
should take on the responsibility
Father entrusted to us.

101
00:07:32,950 --> 00:07:35,750
-What are you doing here?
-What are you doing here?

102
00:07:36,130 --> 00:07:37,730
How would I know why I'm here?

103
00:07:39,370 --> 00:07:41,080
You drank too much yesterday.

104
00:07:43,260 --> 00:07:45,280
You look more like the one
who drank too much.

105
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:46,690
Yesterday, you were

106
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:48,840
yelling and screaming all the time.

107
00:07:50,790 --> 00:07:52,710
I was drunk all day yesterday?

108
00:07:53,030 --> 00:07:53,830
That's right.

109
00:07:57,830 --> 00:07:58,390
Did I

110
00:07:58,630 --> 00:07:59,830
make a fool of myself?

111
00:08:00,190 --> 00:08:01,190
What do you think?

112
00:08:04,510 --> 00:08:05,310
I...

113
00:08:07,390 --> 00:08:09,830
Why did you send me
a jar of wine that night?

114
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:10,600
I...

115
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:13,070
I gave you a jar of wine to send you off.

116
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:15,410
I didn't expect you to get so drunk.

117
00:08:16,710 --> 00:08:18,150
I don't usually drink.

118
00:08:18,220 --> 00:08:20,680
How would I know
what I'm like when I'm drunk?

119
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,850
Did you have a good time last night?

120
00:08:29,070 --> 00:08:29,870
Who are you?

121
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,320
You drank so much
that you lost your memory?

122
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:34,070
You don't remember
what happened yesterday at all?

123
00:08:34,070 --> 00:08:35,309
We met yesterday?

124
00:08:35,490 --> 00:08:36,450
More than that.

125
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:37,880
Actually,

126
00:08:38,620 --> 00:08:39,830
you have to thank me.

127
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,549
What for?

128
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:43,370
I asked him to keep you in the mansion

129
00:08:43,370 --> 00:08:45,340
until his chronic illness is cured.

130
00:08:45,340 --> 00:08:46,400
He also promised to

131
00:08:46,490 --> 00:08:47,820
take you to the capital.

132
00:08:47,910 --> 00:08:48,670
Really?

133
00:08:49,270 --> 00:08:49,820
Zheng.

134
00:08:50,100 --> 00:08:51,370
When did I ever say that?

135
00:08:51,370 --> 00:08:52,800
I can testify.

136
00:08:53,250 --> 00:08:53,710
Really.

137
00:08:54,060 --> 00:08:54,820
That's great.

138
00:08:54,820 --> 00:08:55,490
Come in.

139
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:02,360
This is Imperial Physician Li.

140
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,360
He came here today

141
00:09:03,380 --> 00:09:05,170
to learn from you

142
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,580
how to treat General Xiao's
chronic illness.

143
00:09:07,580 --> 00:09:08,580
I wonder if you

144
00:09:08,610 --> 00:09:10,210
could demonstrate it for us.

145
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,120
Now?

146
00:09:11,390 --> 00:09:12,150
Now.

147
00:09:12,550 --> 00:09:13,360
Now?

148
00:09:14,250 --> 00:09:15,130
Right now.

149
00:10:04,420 --> 00:10:05,350
Lord Fei.

150
00:10:05,370 --> 00:10:06,010
How is it?

151
00:10:06,750 --> 00:10:08,930
The General's pulse is
both weak and strong,

152
00:10:08,930 --> 00:10:10,500
floating on the outside
but sinking inside.

153
00:10:10,500 --> 00:10:13,390
It seems a warm current
is spreading through his body.

154
00:10:13,390 --> 00:10:15,270
I think General has coughed

155
00:10:15,290 --> 00:10:16,770
much less recently.

156
00:10:16,800 --> 00:10:19,600
I didn't expect you to
know so much about medicine.

157
00:10:20,630 --> 00:10:23,120
I have served the royal family
for many years.

158
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:25,390
I have some skill in taking pulses.

159
00:10:26,030 --> 00:10:28,550
But if you want to
cure the General's illness,

160
00:10:28,550 --> 00:10:30,080
acupuncture is not enough.

161
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:32,120
He also needs medicine to recuperate.

162
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,720
Among the many ingredients,

163
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:35,320
the Snow Lotus

164
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:37,390
is the hardest to find.

165
00:10:38,690 --> 00:10:39,290
Of course.

166
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,840
The Snow Lotus is...

167
00:10:40,970 --> 00:10:41,570
By the way.

168
00:10:42,020 --> 00:10:42,820
Your medicine

169
00:10:42,970 --> 00:10:44,700
seems to be missing Snow Lotus.

170
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:46,180
If we can't find it,

171
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:47,880
all previous treatments

172
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,750
will be in vain.

173
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:54,320
When treating someone before,

174
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:56,520
it seemed that I also needed Snow Lotus.

175
00:11:00,620 --> 00:11:01,990
Forget it. Forget it.

176
00:11:02,570 --> 00:11:04,150
But this old imperial doctor

177
00:11:04,150 --> 00:11:06,240
can write the same
prescription as me.

178
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:08,150
It shows your medical skills
are excellent.

179
00:11:08,150 --> 00:11:08,670
My Lord.

180
00:11:09,260 --> 00:11:10,920
This lady's medical practice

181
00:11:11,130 --> 00:11:12,870
is very much like that of

182
00:11:12,940 --> 00:11:15,400
the head imperial physician
many years ago.

183
00:11:15,630 --> 00:11:16,700
She can cure

184
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:19,290
the General's illness alone.

185
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:22,630
May I ask who you learned
your medical skills from?

186
00:11:23,900 --> 00:11:24,970
I

187
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:29,130
taught myself from medical books.

188
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,770
The younger generation

189
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:32,510
will surpass us in time.

190
00:11:34,170 --> 00:11:35,020
Farewell.

191
00:11:38,990 --> 00:11:41,690
The marriage alliance procession
will enter the pass soon.

192
00:11:41,690 --> 00:11:42,690
General Xiao,

193
00:11:43,020 --> 00:11:43,900
get ready.

194
00:11:44,210 --> 00:11:45,340
Don't worry, Zheng.

195
00:11:57,630 --> 00:11:58,630
This carriage is so big.

196
00:11:58,630 --> 00:11:59,480
It's so grand.

197
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:00,240
Too grand.

198
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,150
And too precious.

199
00:12:01,150 --> 00:12:02,030
Yes.

200
00:13:04,210 --> 00:13:06,790
[General's Mansion]

201
00:13:21,040 --> 00:13:22,440
[Princess of Changmo, Jiang Wanyu]

202
00:13:32,420 --> 00:13:33,300
Jin Xi.

203
00:13:35,130 --> 00:13:35,860
Here you are.

204
00:13:37,380 --> 00:13:38,380
What is this?

205
00:13:38,590 --> 00:13:40,050
Though you are my patient,

206
00:13:40,220 --> 00:13:42,530
I have regarded you as my sister.

207
00:13:42,950 --> 00:13:43,500
This is

208
00:13:43,890 --> 00:13:46,090
the prescription I'm giving you.

209
00:13:46,550 --> 00:13:48,100
If you get hurt again,

210
00:13:48,130 --> 00:13:50,590
you can get the medicine
and treat yourself.

211
00:13:53,140 --> 00:13:56,070
Three years ago, Jin Xi left
without saying goodbye.

212
00:13:56,390 --> 00:13:58,590
How did she become the Princess's maid?

213
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:03,370
Please stop, my lords.

214
00:14:03,370 --> 00:14:04,970
Her Highness is taking a nap.

215
00:14:05,010 --> 00:14:05,860
Who are you?

216
00:14:06,020 --> 00:14:08,530
I am the female official
of Her Highness for the marriage alliance.

217
00:14:08,530 --> 00:14:10,260
General, you can call me Jin Xi.

218
00:14:11,150 --> 00:14:12,010
I didn't expect

219
00:14:12,310 --> 00:14:13,610
the female official from Changmo

220
00:14:13,610 --> 00:14:15,060
to be so full of energy.

221
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:16,920
Her Highness is about to get married soon.

222
00:14:16,920 --> 00:14:18,430
Then why such negligence?

223
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:19,940
Her Highness is of noble birth.

224
00:14:19,940 --> 00:14:22,090
The journey to Tianlang Pass
was exhausting.

225
00:14:22,090 --> 00:14:23,150
She wants to sleep a little longer,

226
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:24,940
and I'm sure you lords can understand.

227
00:14:24,940 --> 00:14:27,240
Besides, guards have already been posted.

228
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:29,120
What do you lords want now?

229
00:14:29,450 --> 00:14:30,910
It's a misunderstanding.

230
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:31,910
Posting guards

231
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:33,980
is for Her Highness's safety.

232
00:14:34,290 --> 00:14:35,820
We want to meet Her Highness

233
00:14:35,930 --> 00:14:37,570
simply to follow protocol.

234
00:14:37,690 --> 00:14:39,410
Once the relevant matters are settled,

235
00:14:39,410 --> 00:14:42,050
we can depart for the capital
as soon as possible.

236
00:14:42,050 --> 00:14:44,070
And Her Highness
can meet His Majesty sooner.

237
00:14:44,070 --> 00:14:44,600
That way,

238
00:14:45,140 --> 00:14:46,770
the marriage alliance will be perfect.

239
00:14:46,770 --> 00:14:47,930
My Lady,

240
00:14:48,100 --> 00:14:49,030
don't you agree?

241
00:14:49,380 --> 00:14:50,140
Jin Xi,

242
00:14:50,450 --> 00:14:51,340
let them in.

243
00:14:51,500 --> 00:14:52,020
Yes.

244
00:14:56,860 --> 00:14:58,020
Princess Peace.

245
00:14:58,380 --> 00:14:59,500
It's a nice title.

246
00:14:59,810 --> 00:15:01,020
My father hopes that

247
00:15:01,020 --> 00:15:04,020
Changmo and Jinglan
are close and friendly countries

248
00:15:04,290 --> 00:15:05,340
with no more wars.

249
00:15:05,410 --> 00:15:07,140
That is why he chose this title.

250
00:15:10,980 --> 00:15:12,640
Please take a look, General Xiao.

251
00:15:12,640 --> 00:15:13,430
No need.

252
00:15:14,620 --> 00:15:16,140
The royal genealogy might be real,

253
00:15:16,140 --> 00:15:17,480
but the person might not be.

254
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:19,260
Please take off your veil, Your Highness,

255
00:15:19,260 --> 00:15:20,690
and let us see your true face.

256
00:15:20,690 --> 00:15:22,420
Your concerns are reasonable.

257
00:15:23,770 --> 00:15:25,170
Help me take off the veil.

258
00:15:25,380 --> 00:15:25,860
Yes.

259
00:15:39,220 --> 00:15:39,930
Lord Fei.

260
00:15:40,190 --> 00:15:41,790
According to the marriage
alliance process,

261
00:15:41,790 --> 00:15:42,990
what is the next step?

262
00:15:44,300 --> 00:15:45,060
Body search.

263
00:15:47,620 --> 00:15:48,340
Doctor Han,

264
00:15:48,340 --> 00:15:48,980
Miss Han,

265
00:15:48,980 --> 00:15:49,860
Madam Han,

266
00:15:49,860 --> 00:15:51,020
please help me.

267
00:15:51,380 --> 00:15:53,110
I'm here to treat your general.

268
00:15:53,220 --> 00:15:54,450
I'm not a maid in the mansion.

269
00:15:54,450 --> 00:15:56,100
Isn't treating his illness
and saving his life enough?

270
00:15:56,100 --> 00:15:57,410
He still wants to order me around.

271
00:15:57,410 --> 00:15:57,900
Would he dare?

272
00:15:57,900 --> 00:15:58,680
He wouldn't dare.

273
00:15:58,680 --> 00:15:59,770
He wouldn't dare order you around.

274
00:15:59,770 --> 00:16:01,050
He... He is begging for your help.

275
00:16:01,050 --> 00:16:02,220
If he wanted my help,

276
00:16:02,570 --> 00:16:03,780
why didn't he come himself?

277
00:16:03,780 --> 00:16:04,260
He...

278
00:16:05,320 --> 00:16:07,320
He thinks his relationship with you

279
00:16:07,340 --> 00:16:08,600
isn't as close as ours.

280
00:16:09,050 --> 00:16:10,780
She is the Princess of Changmo.

281
00:16:11,050 --> 00:16:12,380
Searching a Princess

282
00:16:12,650 --> 00:16:14,290
isn't something commoners like us can do.

283
00:16:14,290 --> 00:16:15,620
No matter what,

284
00:16:15,620 --> 00:16:16,710
you both are women.

285
00:16:17,020 --> 00:16:17,620
Physician Han,

286
00:16:17,620 --> 00:16:18,620
help me!

287
00:16:18,620 --> 00:16:20,550
Otherwise, I can't finish my task.

288
00:16:22,570 --> 00:16:23,290
All right.

289
00:16:23,620 --> 00:16:24,980
I'll do it as a favor to you.

290
00:16:24,980 --> 00:16:26,180
Thank you. Thank you.

291
00:16:27,350 --> 00:16:27,980
Lead the way.

292
00:16:27,980 --> 00:16:28,440
Please.

293
00:16:30,810 --> 00:16:31,610
I'll go first.

294
00:16:35,890 --> 00:16:36,500
General,

295
00:16:36,560 --> 00:16:37,820
Physician Han is here.

296
00:16:43,730 --> 00:16:44,330
Thank you.

297
00:16:44,930 --> 00:16:45,930
Then don't forget

298
00:16:46,170 --> 00:16:47,620
to repay me, General Xiao.

299
00:16:47,620 --> 00:16:48,350
Definitely.

300
00:16:52,260 --> 00:16:53,320
How could it be her?

301
00:16:53,690 --> 00:16:55,500
Later, search her thoroughly

302
00:16:55,500 --> 00:16:56,380
for things

303
00:16:57,260 --> 00:16:58,610
like silver needles, a short sword,

304
00:16:58,610 --> 00:16:59,410
or poison.

305
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:01,570
Understood.

306
00:17:05,170 --> 00:17:06,700
Greetings, Your Highness.

307
00:17:06,730 --> 00:17:07,540
Who is this?

308
00:17:07,819 --> 00:17:09,099
This is Physician Han.

309
00:17:09,730 --> 00:17:10,839
She is also from Changmo, like you.

310
00:17:10,839 --> 00:17:12,020
Having her search Your Highness

311
00:17:12,020 --> 00:17:13,380
wouldn't be disrespectful to you.

312
00:17:13,380 --> 00:17:14,569
To serve Your Highness

313
00:17:14,569 --> 00:17:15,569
is my honor.

314
00:17:21,170 --> 00:17:23,619
A body search inevitably
requires taking off clothes.

315
00:17:23,619 --> 00:17:25,349
Are you two planning to sit here

316
00:17:25,450 --> 00:17:26,319
and watch?

317
00:17:27,250 --> 00:17:28,180
If I don't watch,

318
00:17:28,210 --> 00:17:29,060
how do I know

319
00:17:29,060 --> 00:17:30,280
if you search carefully?

320
00:17:30,280 --> 00:17:31,480
If you don't trust me,

321
00:17:31,820 --> 00:17:32,750
then I'll leave.

322
00:17:32,880 --> 00:17:33,580
Physician Han.

323
00:17:33,580 --> 00:17:34,380
Wait a moment.

324
00:17:53,860 --> 00:17:55,360
How could
the dignified Princess of Changmo

325
00:17:55,360 --> 00:17:57,250
carry anything bad?

326
00:17:57,690 --> 00:17:59,550
There's no need for a body search.

327
00:18:00,740 --> 00:18:02,470
However, this female official

328
00:18:04,730 --> 00:18:06,730
needs to be thoroughly checked.

329
00:18:07,060 --> 00:18:08,690
Why should you search me?

330
00:18:08,690 --> 00:18:10,350
If you don't let me search you,

331
00:18:10,410 --> 00:18:12,010
those men outside

332
00:18:12,010 --> 00:18:13,380
will have to do it.

333
00:18:15,140 --> 00:18:16,410
Since I must be searched,

334
00:18:16,410 --> 00:18:17,820
go ahead, Physician Han.

335
00:18:20,450 --> 00:18:21,100
Okay.

336
00:18:21,540 --> 00:18:22,540
Pardon me.

337
00:18:31,860 --> 00:18:32,820
Come in.

338
00:18:42,630 --> 00:18:43,630
What did you find?

339
00:18:43,730 --> 00:18:45,450
A dignified peace-making princess

340
00:18:45,450 --> 00:18:47,510
wouldn't bring anything forbidden.

341
00:18:47,860 --> 00:18:49,380
Not to mention the princess,

342
00:18:49,380 --> 00:18:51,540
I even searched her personal maid.

343
00:18:51,860 --> 00:18:53,100
I found nothing.

344
00:18:53,380 --> 00:18:54,690
It is you

345
00:18:55,170 --> 00:18:56,580
who are being petty.

346
00:18:59,820 --> 00:19:00,930
Pardon my intrusion.

347
00:19:00,930 --> 00:19:02,860
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

348
00:19:03,380 --> 00:19:05,180
Lord Fei is just doing your duty.

349
00:19:05,730 --> 00:19:07,650
Besides, this physician
did everything properly,

350
00:19:07,650 --> 00:19:09,250
so there is no offense taken.

351
00:19:13,780 --> 00:19:15,140
What do you think

352
00:19:15,330 --> 00:19:17,260
about the peace-making princess?

353
00:19:17,340 --> 00:19:18,710
I didn't expect Changmo barbarians

354
00:19:18,710 --> 00:19:19,660
to have

355
00:19:19,860 --> 00:19:20,930
such a princess.

356
00:19:22,300 --> 00:19:24,540
But the female official beside her...

357
00:19:26,650 --> 00:19:28,450
What about the female official?

358
00:19:29,460 --> 00:19:31,450
We are high-ranking officials of Jinglan.

359
00:19:31,450 --> 00:19:32,970
Her Highness is well-informed,

360
00:19:32,970 --> 00:19:35,570
but this female official
didn't panic either.

361
00:19:35,730 --> 00:19:36,460
She must have

362
00:19:36,890 --> 00:19:38,240
been through a lot.

363
00:19:40,580 --> 00:19:41,300
What else?

364
00:19:41,930 --> 00:19:43,330
She's a female official.

365
00:19:43,450 --> 00:19:44,990
The princess's dowry officials

366
00:19:44,990 --> 00:19:46,520
don't need to do heavy work.

367
00:19:46,650 --> 00:19:49,710
But she seems to have
removed the calluses on her hands.

368
00:19:51,020 --> 00:19:53,480
I didn't expect you
to observe so carefully.

369
00:19:53,580 --> 00:19:56,140
Changmo has been sending
spies to our country for years.

370
00:19:56,140 --> 00:19:57,690
I've been fighting them for years.

371
00:19:57,690 --> 00:19:58,820
I did many different things

372
00:19:58,820 --> 00:20:00,060
from a relaxed official like you

373
00:20:00,060 --> 00:20:02,340
who stays in the court every day.

374
00:20:04,010 --> 00:20:04,690
Okay.

375
00:20:05,490 --> 00:20:06,340
Then，

376
00:20:06,820 --> 00:20:08,620
how do you plan to deal with them?

377
00:20:08,820 --> 00:20:09,930
Didn't I just say?

378
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:10,630
Tonight,

379
00:20:10,650 --> 00:20:11,720
you should have a drink with the princess.

380
00:20:11,720 --> 00:20:12,510
Me?

381
00:20:13,860 --> 00:20:14,930
Why?

382
00:20:15,060 --> 00:20:15,930
As a host,

383
00:20:16,210 --> 00:20:18,210
treating guests from afar to a meal

384
00:20:18,350 --> 00:20:19,380
is normal.

385
00:20:19,780 --> 00:20:20,980
And I've always known

386
00:20:21,130 --> 00:20:21,710
Lord Fei

387
00:20:21,780 --> 00:20:23,650
can hold your liquor.

388
00:20:24,380 --> 00:20:25,650
Why do I feel like

389
00:20:25,650 --> 00:20:27,310
you're not telling the truth?

390
00:20:28,620 --> 00:20:29,780
People tell the truth after drinking.

391
00:20:29,780 --> 00:20:31,340
I will host the banquet,
and you can drink with them.

392
00:20:31,340 --> 00:20:33,450
That's a chance to investigate the spies.

393
00:20:33,450 --> 00:20:34,340
Seize it.

394
00:20:38,490 --> 00:20:39,350
Your Highness,

395
00:20:39,540 --> 00:20:41,070
you're slacking off again.

396
00:20:41,820 --> 00:20:43,390
It's just you and me here.

397
00:20:43,730 --> 00:20:45,060
Who am I performing for?

398
00:20:45,210 --> 00:20:46,810
Sit down and rest for a while.

399
00:20:47,730 --> 00:20:49,190
That's against the rules.

400
00:20:49,250 --> 00:20:50,250
Rules. Rules.

401
00:20:50,690 --> 00:20:51,950
All you know are rules.

402
00:20:52,170 --> 00:20:52,970
So annoying.

403
00:20:55,970 --> 00:20:57,970
I wish Liu Chu were the sort of person

404
00:20:57,970 --> 00:21:00,370
who doesn't follow the rules,
just like me.

405
00:21:03,840 --> 00:21:04,810
Jin Xi.

406
00:21:06,340 --> 00:21:08,210
You've been with me for so many years.

407
00:21:08,210 --> 00:21:10,070
Why haven't I ever seen you smile?

408
00:21:10,410 --> 00:21:12,340
There's nothing to be happy about.

409
00:21:12,340 --> 00:21:14,940
But if we could leave
for the capital tomorrow,

410
00:21:15,210 --> 00:21:16,410
then I might smile.

411
00:21:17,300 --> 00:21:18,970
I don't want to go that early.

412
00:21:19,410 --> 00:21:20,820
I'm not ready yet.

413
00:21:22,860 --> 00:21:23,490
All right.

414
00:21:23,490 --> 00:21:24,340
You can go out first.

415
00:21:24,340 --> 00:21:25,670
Leave me alone for a while.

416
00:21:25,670 --> 00:21:26,280
Yes.

417
00:21:41,930 --> 00:21:43,260
You did me a great favor.

418
00:21:43,990 --> 00:21:45,520
Let me treat you to some tea.

419
00:21:50,980 --> 00:21:52,260
It's snowing again.

420
00:21:56,300 --> 00:21:57,650
Why do Changmo and Jinglan

421
00:21:57,650 --> 00:21:59,250
have to fight?

422
00:22:00,540 --> 00:22:01,780
If there were peace,

423
00:22:02,210 --> 00:22:03,470
why would there be war?

424
00:22:03,650 --> 00:22:06,250
Changmo has been attacking
Jinglan all year round.

425
00:22:06,250 --> 00:22:08,900
It's why we built the Tianlang Pass.

426
00:22:10,580 --> 00:22:11,900
But even so,

427
00:22:12,250 --> 00:22:14,180
they still want to attack the city.

428
00:22:15,820 --> 00:22:17,620
You've never lived in Changmo.

429
00:22:18,380 --> 00:22:21,140
Most of the lands beyond the northern
border are deserts.

430
00:22:21,140 --> 00:22:22,870
If there's a natural disaster,

431
00:22:23,010 --> 00:22:24,730
both people and livestock
will starve to death.

432
00:22:24,730 --> 00:22:25,990
If they could survive,

433
00:22:26,410 --> 00:22:28,900
who would risk their lives to fight a war?

434
00:22:30,970 --> 00:22:31,730
What you said

435
00:22:32,620 --> 00:22:33,490
makes sense.

436
00:22:37,820 --> 00:22:39,250
You have been fighting for years.

437
00:22:39,250 --> 00:22:41,170
How could you know
the suffering of us commoners?

438
00:22:41,170 --> 00:22:42,690
Peace is so precious.

439
00:22:42,730 --> 00:22:43,730
I want to know.

440
00:22:44,930 --> 00:22:46,330
Have you stayed by my side

441
00:22:47,010 --> 00:22:48,410
just to treat my illness?

442
00:22:48,860 --> 00:22:50,210
I am a physician.

443
00:22:50,350 --> 00:22:52,210
I need to prove my medical skills.

444
00:22:52,490 --> 00:22:54,690
And you also have to pay my medical fees.

445
00:22:55,340 --> 00:22:56,540
No other reasons?

446
00:22:57,820 --> 00:22:59,220
What else could there be?

447
00:23:03,250 --> 00:23:04,340
Tell me,

448
00:23:04,620 --> 00:23:05,860
how could there be

449
00:23:05,860 --> 00:23:07,790
such a strange thing in this world?

450
00:23:08,060 --> 00:23:10,300
We're good friends who haven't
seen each other for years.

451
00:23:10,300 --> 00:23:12,830
But she didn't recognize me
when we met again.

452
00:23:14,780 --> 00:23:15,580
Yes.

453
00:23:17,250 --> 00:23:18,850
Why didn't she recognize me?

454
00:23:19,750 --> 00:23:22,100
Maybe a fever ruined her brain,

455
00:23:22,780 --> 00:23:24,780
or she accidentally hurt her head,

456
00:23:25,540 --> 00:23:26,970
or she got some kind of

457
00:23:26,970 --> 00:23:28,230
amnesia or something.

458
00:23:31,140 --> 00:23:31,860
Then,

459
00:23:32,410 --> 00:23:33,540
when you were young,

460
00:23:33,540 --> 00:23:35,780
did you hurt your head

461
00:23:35,930 --> 00:23:37,130
and lose your memory?

462
00:23:38,450 --> 00:23:40,170
My second uncle said that
when I was a teenager,

463
00:23:40,170 --> 00:23:41,300
my head was injured.

464
00:23:43,860 --> 00:23:45,540
Then, did you

465
00:23:45,860 --> 00:23:47,490
forget any important friends
due to that?

466
00:23:47,490 --> 00:23:48,700
How is that possible?

467
00:23:48,970 --> 00:23:49,450
I...

468
00:23:54,170 --> 00:23:55,630
Why are you asking so much?

469
00:23:55,970 --> 00:23:56,650
Nothing.

470
00:23:56,980 --> 00:23:57,710
Just asking.

471
00:24:01,860 --> 00:24:03,610
Is it that good?

472
00:24:05,570 --> 00:24:06,300
Let me try it.

473
00:24:08,340 --> 00:24:09,270
Can you drink it?

474
00:24:20,860 --> 00:24:22,410
It doesn't taste that good.

475
00:24:25,170 --> 00:24:26,370
I'm going home first.

476
00:24:32,370 --> 00:24:33,100
Are you okay?

477
00:24:42,450 --> 00:24:43,210
I didn't expect that

478
00:24:43,210 --> 00:24:43,930
you even knew this trick.

479
00:24:43,930 --> 00:24:45,860
I also know grappling techniques.

480
00:24:55,140 --> 00:24:57,140
She really passed out after one sip.

481
00:25:06,150 --> 00:25:07,040
General.

482
00:25:09,450 --> 00:25:10,300
What's up?

483
00:25:10,570 --> 00:25:11,830
She got drunk on water?

484
00:25:12,170 --> 00:25:12,730
She...

485
00:25:14,820 --> 00:25:15,260
She...

486
00:25:15,620 --> 00:25:18,150
She can't even drink
a single drop of alcohol.

487
00:25:18,340 --> 00:25:18,860
Sir,

488
00:25:19,100 --> 00:25:20,300
the banquet is ready.

489
00:25:20,450 --> 00:25:22,980
Lord Fei and Her Highness
are already inside.

490
00:25:23,140 --> 00:25:23,730
Okay.

491
00:25:24,290 --> 00:25:24,850
Tonight,

492
00:25:25,010 --> 00:25:26,060
take your cues from me.

493
00:25:26,060 --> 00:25:26,490
Yes.

494
00:25:27,210 --> 00:25:28,140
There's wine.

495
00:25:30,380 --> 00:25:30,820
You.

496
00:25:31,730 --> 00:25:32,340
Come on.

497
00:25:32,540 --> 00:25:33,670
Watch out.

498
00:25:34,140 --> 00:25:34,740
Slow down.

499
00:25:35,140 --> 00:25:35,820
Slow down.

500
00:25:40,170 --> 00:25:40,690
Zheng.

501
00:25:41,170 --> 00:25:41,770
Princess.

502
00:25:41,860 --> 00:25:42,690
I'm the host tonight.

503
00:25:42,690 --> 00:25:43,420
But I'm late.

504
00:25:43,580 --> 00:25:45,440
Sorry for that. I'll drink first.

505
00:25:47,780 --> 00:25:49,240
After you, Your Highness.

506
00:25:54,060 --> 00:25:55,060
We haven't reached the capital yet.

507
00:25:55,060 --> 00:25:56,340
You've worked hard, Lord Fei.

508
00:25:56,340 --> 00:25:57,370
I offer you a toast.

509
00:25:57,370 --> 00:25:59,010
As the special envoy
for the marriage alliance,

510
00:25:59,010 --> 00:26:00,820
it is my utmost honor.

511
00:26:04,210 --> 00:26:05,650
Visitors from afar are guests.

512
00:26:05,650 --> 00:26:06,620
My Lady,

513
00:26:06,970 --> 00:26:08,970
why don't you toast Lord Fei as well?

514
00:26:11,250 --> 00:26:12,340
That's right, Jin Xi.

515
00:26:12,340 --> 00:26:13,690
Toast Lord Fei too.

516
00:26:15,190 --> 00:26:15,790
Yes.

517
00:26:21,060 --> 00:26:21,590
Lord Fei,

518
00:26:22,080 --> 00:26:23,540
before I offer this toast,

519
00:26:23,690 --> 00:26:25,100
I still want to know

520
00:26:25,340 --> 00:26:27,270
when we can depart for the capital.

521
00:26:27,380 --> 00:26:28,930
I have made it very clear.

522
00:26:29,170 --> 00:26:31,300
We must wait for His Majesty's decree.

523
00:26:31,410 --> 00:26:33,740
What if His Majesty never issues a decree?

524
00:26:33,820 --> 00:26:35,620
Must Her Highness keep waiting?

525
00:26:38,410 --> 00:26:40,340
It seems that is the only way.

526
00:26:45,140 --> 00:26:45,800
Chengfeng,

527
00:26:46,170 --> 00:26:47,300
you're just in time.

528
00:26:47,490 --> 00:26:48,730
Perform a sword dance for everyone

529
00:26:48,730 --> 00:26:49,790
to liven things up.

530
00:26:50,220 --> 00:26:51,420
Yes, General.

531
00:27:18,060 --> 00:27:20,100
Wait, why are you fighting?

532
00:27:24,060 --> 00:27:26,340
Why are you bullying a weak woman?

533
00:27:26,820 --> 00:27:27,480
Chengfeng.

534
00:27:27,800 --> 00:27:28,250
Yes.

535
00:27:28,280 --> 00:27:28,940
Apologize.

536
00:27:31,410 --> 00:27:31,930
Yes.

537
00:27:34,100 --> 00:27:35,100
My Lady,

538
00:27:35,490 --> 00:27:36,250
I

539
00:27:36,520 --> 00:27:37,850
accidentally slipped.

540
00:27:37,970 --> 00:27:38,490
Sorry.

541
00:27:40,330 --> 00:27:41,190
Physician Han.

542
00:27:41,470 --> 00:27:43,650
General Chengfeng has already apologized.

543
00:27:43,650 --> 00:27:45,380
Why don't you take a seat first?

544
00:27:47,100 --> 00:27:48,060
Report!

545
00:27:48,910 --> 00:27:50,540
Ms. Tang requests an audience.

546
00:27:50,540 --> 00:27:51,410
Show them in.

547
00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:51,960
Yes.

548
00:27:55,100 --> 00:27:56,140
Xiao Chi.

549
00:27:56,580 --> 00:27:59,060
Why didn't you invite me
to drink with you?

550
00:27:59,410 --> 00:27:59,940
Ms. Tang.

551
00:28:00,140 --> 00:28:01,200
Please take a seat.

552
00:28:02,140 --> 00:28:03,450
What

553
00:28:03,540 --> 00:28:04,870
brought you here today?

554
00:28:05,170 --> 00:28:05,900
What?

555
00:28:06,450 --> 00:28:08,250
You owe me a romantic debt,

556
00:28:08,380 --> 00:28:09,450
but you're ignoring me now?

557
00:28:09,450 --> 00:28:10,100
Ms. Tang.

558
00:28:10,410 --> 00:28:11,650
Don't talk

559
00:28:11,860 --> 00:28:12,880
nonsense.

560
00:28:13,380 --> 00:28:14,010
I

561
00:28:14,140 --> 00:28:15,690
want to marry Xiao Chi

562
00:28:15,930 --> 00:28:17,660
like all the women in this city.

563
00:28:18,010 --> 00:28:19,100
So, you

564
00:28:19,170 --> 00:28:21,010
owe a romantic debt to all of us.

565
00:28:23,210 --> 00:28:24,010
Ms. Tang,

566
00:28:24,490 --> 00:28:25,620
let me properly introduce you

567
00:28:25,620 --> 00:28:26,950
everyone present here.

568
00:28:27,780 --> 00:28:29,680
This is the Minister of Revenue,

569
00:28:30,100 --> 00:28:31,230
Fei Zheng, Lord Fei.

570
00:28:34,210 --> 00:28:35,970
This is the Princess of Changmo.

571
00:28:35,970 --> 00:28:38,540
Your Highness is indeed a great beauty.

572
00:28:39,410 --> 00:28:41,410
This is Physician Han.

573
00:28:42,930 --> 00:28:43,790
Physician Han.

574
00:28:46,380 --> 00:28:48,900
And this is the famous person
in our Tianlang Pass...

575
00:28:48,900 --> 00:28:50,010
I am Tang Zhaoxue.

576
00:28:50,170 --> 00:28:51,770
All the inns in Tianlang Pass

577
00:28:51,900 --> 00:28:52,820
are run by me.

578
00:28:53,270 --> 00:28:54,030
Zheng.

579
00:28:54,820 --> 00:28:56,650
When there was a famine at Tianlang Pass,

580
00:28:56,650 --> 00:28:57,980
Ms. Tang helped us a lot.

581
00:28:59,900 --> 00:29:01,030
I didn't expect that

582
00:29:01,170 --> 00:29:02,860
Ms. Tang is not only beautiful,

583
00:29:02,860 --> 00:29:03,870
but also very kind.

584
00:29:03,870 --> 00:29:05,550
Then I will be bold enough

585
00:29:06,000 --> 00:29:07,190
to toast you all.

586
00:29:11,410 --> 00:29:12,270
Physician Han.

587
00:29:13,730 --> 00:29:15,390
You'd better not drink today.

588
00:29:19,620 --> 00:29:21,690
The imperial decree has arrived.

589
00:29:22,900 --> 00:29:24,580
The Emperor has issued a decree.

590
00:29:24,580 --> 00:29:27,170
Everyone has to kneel to receive it.

591
00:29:28,900 --> 00:29:30,170
The Emperor commands

592
00:29:30,380 --> 00:29:32,580
that the special envoy
for the marriage alliance, Fei Zheng,

593
00:29:32,580 --> 00:29:35,820
immediately lead the alliance procession
back to the capital.

594
00:29:35,820 --> 00:29:37,300
No delays are allowed.

595
00:29:37,650 --> 00:29:40,650
General Xiao Chi
should escort them personally

596
00:29:40,650 --> 00:29:42,210
and return together.

597
00:29:42,210 --> 00:29:43,730
Respect this.

598
00:29:46,900 --> 00:29:48,580
I receive the decree.
